### Get all recettes to verify creation
GET {{url}}/api/recettes
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get specific recette by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
GET {{url}}/api/recettes/{id}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Update specific recette by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
PUT {{url}}/api/recettes/{id}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "data": {
    "description": "Updated description for the recipe."
  }
}


### Delete specific recette by ID (replace {id} with actual ID)
DELETE {{url}}/api/recettes/{id}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}